@startuml
title Deployment Diagram - Blazing Darkness AS-IS

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

actor "Player" as User

node "User Computer" as PC {
  node "Terminal / Console" as Terminal {
    artifact "BlazingDarkness.exe" as EXE
    artifact "stdout / stdin" as IO
  }

  folder "Local Runtime Environment" as Runtime {
    artifact "terminal settings\n(raw mode, VT mode)" as TermState
    artifact "game session state\n(in memory)" as Session
  }
}

User --> Terminal : interacts
Terminal --> EXE : starts
EXE --> IO : reads input / writes output
EXE --> TermState : setRawMode(), enableVTMode()
EXE --> Session : updates player/world state

@enduml
